{"tid":2024204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳皓桓籲續關注被捕同道","createTime":"2020-05-19T12:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T13:20:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1376b80073bb44380fa0e2ad157eca62fdf787dd","tid":2024204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200519/7IAJXCXD6EBSADWRGDOG4ECB5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2F7IAJXCXD6EBSADWRGDOG4ECB5E%2F&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7nKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=92a70a2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200519%2F7IAJXCXD6EBSADWRGDOG4ECB5E%2F&h=698d5826\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200519/7IAJXCXD6EBSADWRGDOG4ECB5E/</a><br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓籲續關注被捕同道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200519/large/1589820257_e6c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200519%2Flarge%2F1589820257_e6c5.jpg&h=6964f039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳皓桓<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民主派元老級人馬李柱銘、吳靄儀等首被控，吸引近百中外記者採訪，到庭聲援市民逼爆法庭，當眾人和律師團隊步出法庭，報以掌聲歡送，並高叫「五大訴求，缺一不可」等。最年輕的被告、民陣副召集人陳皓桓指面對打壓，港人不會放棄追求民主自由公義的決心，呼籲市民繼續關注被捕及羈押的同道。<br />\n<br />\n一眾被告等候開庭期間神情輕鬆，互相寒暄問暖，其中單仲偕、梁耀忠等說笑，問誰人「處男下海」。單更透露本案下次聆訊當日適逢他六十大壽，「賀我大壽」。<br />\n戴耀廷：打壓激發更多人抗爭<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：泛民15人提堂 5人加控煽惑罪  「港人不會被嚇退」<br />\n<br />\n在同一法庭經歷審訊的「佔中三子」戴耀廷、陳健民和朱耀明，昨亦有到庭。戴表示，<br />\n.....................................<br />\n而是探討禮崩樂壞之後如何重建法治秩序。<br />\n<br />\n昨有數十名警員在場戒備，逾20名包括香港政研會在內的藍絲團體在庭外高呼「重判黎智英」等口號，但他們一度把朱耀明牧師錯認作黎，<br />\n.......................................<br />\n一眾聲援市民不斷向法院外駐守的警員大喊「黑警死全家」及「死黑警」，其間一名法院保安衝出並叫眾人停止叫口號，多名市民圍罵該保安並勸他「做好人」，保安最終遭同事勸退及拉走。<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊思雅、劉偉琪"},{"pid":"a01e5b383105d7495dd5c3e1e5f411ed3d696286","tid":2024204,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T12:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24257f82826079765d75baab26695aa557fa48a","tid":2024204,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}